OL,5, TV producer Beryl Vertue, whose company
OL,6, created the series Men Behaving Badly  
OL,7, and Sherlock, has died aged 90.        
OL,9,FThe media executive, who rose to the   
OL,10,Ftop of the industry after starting as a
OL,11,Fsecretary, "passed away peacefully" on 
OL,12,FSaturday, her family said.             
OL,14,FIndustry colleagues called her one of  
OL,15,Fthe most influential women in British  
OL,16,FTV.                                    
OL,18,FDaughters Sue and Debbie, producers at 
OL,19,Fthe company their mother founded, said:
OL,20,F"She meant so much to so many."        
